data.description: **PRE-INSPECTED** Welcome to this beautifully updated home in highly sought after Harvey Oaks. You'll be welcomed by a spacious entryway, leading to a large family room with new carpet and fireplace.  Formal living room and dining room with Brazilian Cherry floors.  Large kitchen with some updated appliances.  New interior doors and hardware throughout.     Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms with newer carpet and paint.  Updated bathrooms on the second floor.  The lower level offers the perfect game room, space for entertainment or in-home office.  The covered deck overlooks a large fenced yard with newer shed.  Close to shopping, schools and amenities.
